headline: Markem-Imaje Unveils SmartLase UV500 5-Watt UV Laser Coder for Marking and Coding
summary: Markem-Imaje, part of Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a global provider of end-to-end supply chain solutions and industrial marking and coding systems, today announced the launch of the SmartLase® UV500, a new 5-watt UV laser printer that is well suited for high-density and delicate materials including hard plastics, recyclable films, metal, and glass. This new printer complements Markem-Imaje's CO2 and Fiber laser portfolio.
